OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782456514
OL,3,CTeenager charged with murder following
OL,4,Cdiscovery of missing girl's body
OL,6,FA 14-year-old boy has been charged
OL,7,Fwith murder following the discovery of
OL,8,Fa missing 14-year-old girl's body,
OL,9,FGwent Police said.
OL,11,FThe teenager, from the Blaenau Gwent
OL,12,Farea, was arrested following the
OL,13,Fdiscovery of the body in the Duffryn
OL,14,FPark area of Blaina on June 22.
OL,16,FFormal identification has not taken
OL,17,Fpolice, but police said the body is
OL,18,Fbelieved to be that of a 14-year-old
OL,19,Fmissing girl called Lilly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
