CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782456514
OL,3,CTeenager charged with murder following
OL,4,Cdiscovery of missing girl's body
OL,6,FThe teenager, described by police as
OL,7,Fwhite British who cannot be named for
OL,8,Flegal reasons, is in custody and will
OL,9,Fappear at Newport Magistrates' Court
OL,10,Fon Friday.
OL,12,FPolice said they were releasing
OL,13,FLilly's name with her family's
OL,14,Fknowledge because it will form part of
OL,15,Fthe court proceedings.
OL,17,FShe had been reported missing having
OL,18,Flast been seen in High Street, Blaina,
OL,19,Fat around 6.50pm on Saturday June 20.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
