OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782456514
OL,3,CTeenager charged with murder following
OL,4,Cdiscovery of missing girl's body
OL,6,FParts of Pilgrims Park, which is
OL,7,Fadjacent to the A467 in Blaina, were
OL,8,Fcordoned off after the body was
OL,9,Fdiscovered.
OL,11,FFloral tributes were left close to the
OL,12,Fscene by members of the public.
OL,14,FDetective Chief Inspector Steven
OL,15,FThomas said: "Our thoughts are with
OL,16,Fthe family and friends of Lilly at
OL,17,Fthis difficult time.
OL,19,F"We understand that there has been a
OL,20,Fgreat deal of interest in this ongoing
OL,21,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@wD@NOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
