PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782456514
OL,3,CTeenager charged with murder following
OL,4,Cdiscovery of missing girl's body
OL,6,F"Examinations of scenes will be
OL,7,Fcontinuing over the coming days,
OL,8,Fincluding at Duffryn Park, where
OL,9,Fcordons remain in place.
OL,11,F"I would like to thank local residents
OL,12,Ffor their continued support and those
OL,13,Fimpacted by the cordons for their
OL,14,Fpatience during this time."
OL,16,FPolice are asking anyone with CCTV
OL,17,Ffootage or information which could
OL,18,Fhelp the investigation to speak to
OL,19,Fofficers, contact them via 101,
OL,20,Fquoting reference 2600194414, or
OL,21,Fonline.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@[O]
